            "description": "Non-planar two-loop integral family for the mixed QCD-electroweak corrections to $gg \\to Hg$, with 7 propagators (5 massless, 2 massive with mass $m_V$) and 2 irreducible scalar products. The 61 master integrals satisfy a canonical system of differential equations with a 62-letter alphabet involving 4 square roots. The MIs are expressible in terms of multiple polylogarithms and were computed analytically in arXiv:2006.05510. This paper provides an independent numerical evaluation via generalized power series expansions, with ancillary files for the DE matrices, boundary conditions, and amplitude form factors compatible with DiffExp.",
